      },
    },
  },
});

```


### Environment

x

### Expected behavior

_No response_

### Actual behavior

_No response_

### OpenAPI document (minimal, if applicable)

_No response_

### Additional context

The package was expected to install, but there was a problem publishing the latest tags

### Description

Generated types can contain duplicate union members. While these duplicates don't affect runtime behavior, they create noise in generated code. I have a working fix ready to submit as a PR.

### Configuration (orval.config)

[`samples/react-query/basic/orval.config.ts`](https://github.com/orval-labs/orval/blob/master/samples/react-query/basic/orval.config.ts)

